channel.title: 718/753 error, HELP PLS
channel.description:
hello, i'm trying to play on a 718/753 server with some friends but i got this weird error. i portforwarded, used canyouseeme.org to check if i did it correctly, but when my friends try to connect they get: [code]error_game_js5_connect[/code]
i know this means it doesn't connect but i dont know [b]why[/b] it doesn't connect because everything seems perfectly fine, the port, sub_revision and ip, etc are like they are supposed to be. still they can't connect and the weirdest thing is that i can, also my firewall is off so that isn't blocking the ingoing/outgoing connection. someone got an idea what it could be?
btw, i'm using a foxtrot 718 client and a rune evo v2 source with rune evo v3 cache, everything works perfectly fine for me but not for my friends.
